replies.body:
It's likely an issue where you client isn't connecting to the Server properly, but it's a quick fix! Run through this [Connection Guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) and it should allow you to pick a champion without any issues. 

If you do run into this problem again after running through the guide make sure you reach out to me. 
{{champion:25}}
